  nodeId: 
  lines:
  - speaker: Veil
    text: Yes. They were.
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    extraDelay: 0
  - speaker: Veil
    text: The elders, the priest, your own brother who turned his face.
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    extraDelay: 0
  - speaker: Veil
    text: All of them, right.
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    extraDelay: 0
  - speaker: Veil
    text: And the child? Was he right too?
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    extraDelay: 0
  - speaker: Irai
    text: He is a child.
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    extraDelay: 0
  - speaker: Veil
    text: Then why did you not leave him on the temple steps?
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    extraDelay: 0
  - speaker: Irai
    text: Because he is mine.
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    extraDelay: 0
  - speaker: Veil
    text: Then there is one thing you did not let them name for you.
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    extraDelay: 0
  choices: []
